data.message: Help!!! pleas help. you are blocked my shop ULR,but yours Debugger dont help me,what i need to do? how unblock my shop?

replies.message: Hi Tadas. If you have already tried running your site through our Debugger, you can reach out to our Facebook Developers in order to make sure your website is compliant: http://bit.ly/2vcq6UO. You'll need to click "Go to Direct Support" and follow the instructions to open a support ticket. If you're unable to see this option, you can contact your web developer for support in making changes to your website's source code. Hope this helps! -Ashley
